'''喬納·希爾'''（'''Jonah Hill'''，全名'''Jonah Hill Feldstein'''<ref name="name">{{cite news |title="Superbad" Star A Real Pisser |publisher=The Smoking Gun |date=2007-08-13 |url=http://www.thesmokinggun.com/archive/years/2007/0813072superbad1.html |accessdate=2007-08-18 |archive-date=2009-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090413011204/http://www.thesmokinggun.com/archive/years/2007/0813072superbad1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，生於{{bd|1983年|12月20日}}）是一位[[美國|美國]]男[[演員|演員]]、[[製片|製片]]和[[編劇|編劇]]。時常為[[喜劇片|喜劇片]]配角演出或[[動畫電影|動畫電影]]配音，知名的作品有《[[好孕臨門|好孕臨門]]》（2007年）、《[[馴龍高手|馴龍高手]]》（2010年）、《[[麥克邁：超能壞蛋|麥克邁：超能壞蛋]]》（2010年）、《[[点球成金|点球成金]]》（2011年）、《[[華爾街之狼|華爾街之狼]]》（2013年）、《[[真實的故事|真實的故事]]》（2015年）和《[[火線掏寶|火線掏寶]]》（2016年）。

== 個人生平 ==
喬納·希爾出生於美國[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]洛杉磯的[[猶太|猶太]]家庭<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref>{{cite news|url= https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/jun/05/jonah-hill-who-i-am-22-jump-street|title= Jonah Hill: 'Having a bad day doesn't reflect who I am as a person'|work= The Guardian|date= June 5, 2014|accessdate= April 18, 2018|archive-date= 2020-12-04|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201204042739/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/jun/05/jonah-hill-who-i-am-22-jump-street|dead-url= no}}</ref>。他在一個工作於音樂生意的環境下長大<ref name=silc>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ropeofsilicon.com/article/interview-jonah-hill-talks-music-and-movies-promoting-get-him-to-the-greek |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100608220909/http://www.ropeofsilicon.com/article/interview-jonah-hill-talks-music-and-movies-promoting-get-him-to-the-greek |archive-date=2010-06-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。喬納·希爾是[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref name=":1">{{cite news|url=http://jewishjournal.com/mobile_20111212/100073/|title=Jonah Hill: ‘Moneyball’s’ super-talented, super-nice Jewish boy [VIDEO]|work=Jewish Journal|date=January 11, 2012|accessdate=April 18, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618152336/http://jewishjournal.com/mobile_20111212/100073/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://jewishweek.timesofisrael.com/the-summer-that-judd-apatow-seth-rogen-and-jonah-hill-took-over-mainstream-comedy/|title=The Summer That Judd Apatow, Seth Rogen, Jonah Hill Took Over Mainstream Comedy|work=The Jewish Week|date=July 27, 2017|accessdate=April 23, 2018|archive-date=2019-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190621040901/http://jewishweek.timesofisrael.com/the-summer-that-judd-apatow-seth-rogen-and-jonah-hill-took-over-mainstream-comedy/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://jewishjournal.com/blogs/125815/jonah-hills-not-so-nice-jewish-guy/|title=Jonah Hill’s not-so-nice Jewish guy|author=|last=Pfefferman|first=Naomi|date=January 6, 2014|work=|newspaper=Jewish Journal|accessdate=June 5, 2018|language=|archive-date=2019-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225110004/https://jewishjournal.com/blogs/125815/jonah-hills-not-so-nice-jewish-guy/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/08/12/magazine/12wwln-Q4-t.html|title=Superdude|last=Solomon|first=Deborah|date=August 12, 2007|work=The New York Times|accessdate=June 5, 2018|quote=Jonah Hill: "I'm a nice Jewish boy."|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124092150/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/08/12/magazine/12wwln-Q4-t.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。13歲時，喬納·希爾接受了猶太教的成年禮（Bar Mitzvah）儀式<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm1706767/bio | title=Jonah Hill - Biography | work=IMDb | accessdate=2017-12-31 | archive-date=2020-11-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117101324/https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1706767/bio | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/07/magazine/jonah-hill-is-no-joke.html|title=Jonah Hill Is No Joke|accessdate=April 23, 2018|author=|date=August 4, 2016|last=Young|first=Molly|work=The New York Times|publisher=|quote=Hill had his bar mitzvah, describing him as “destined for something great” and “electric” even at 13, reciting his Torah portion in a prayer shawl.|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108093250/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/07/magazine/jonah-hill-is-no-joke.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite news|url=https://www.jweekly.com/2012/01/27/in-contest-for-nice-jewish-guys-jonah-hill-wins-it/|title=In contest for nice Jewish guys, Jonah Hill wins it|last=Pfefferman|first=Naomi|date=January 27, 2012|work=J. The Jewish News of Northern California|accessdate=July 2, 2018|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125190030/https://www.jweekly.com/2012/01/27/in-contest-for-nice-jewish-guys-jonah-hill-wins-it/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的父親是負責[[槍與玫瑰|槍與玫瑰]]巡迴演唱會的會計師<ref name=silc/>。他的妹妹[[比妮·费尔德斯坦|比妮·费尔德斯坦]]是女演員<ref>{{cite news|url=http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/229277/hello-beanie-feldstein-moment-dolly-lady-bird/|title=Hello, Beanie: Feldstein Having a Moment With ‘Dolly’ and ‘Lady Bird’|work=Jewish Journal|date=January 3, 2018|accessdate=April 18, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618152334/http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/229277/hello-beanie-feldstein-moment-dolly-lady-bird/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ew.com/tv/2018/01/26/beanie-feldstein-lady-bird-audition-crying/|title=Lady Bird's Beanie Feldstein on her great audition and 'relentless weeps' after watching the movie|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=January 26, 2018|accessdate=April 24, 2018|archive-date=2020-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200419060500/https://ew.com/tv/2018/01/26/beanie-feldstein-lady-bird-audition-crying/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他就讀於[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的[[布倫特伍德學校|布倫特伍德學校]]（Brentwood School），畢業於Crossroads School，一所位於[[聖莫尼卡|聖莫尼卡]]的表演學校，眾多好萊塢演員皆在此校就讀。畢業後，喬納·希爾離開加利福尼亞到[[紐約|紐約]]的[[新學院|新學院]]研習表演藝術。他也為慈善企業募款資金<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.crowdrise.com/jonahhill | title=Jonah Hill on Crowdrise | accessdate=2010-04-28 | archive-date=2019-08-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812010248/https://www.crowdrise.com/jonahhill | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 事業 ==
大學時期，希爾開始為他自己的表演寫劇本，並在[[紐約|紐約]]鄰近東村的小吧演出<ref name="htc">"[http://www.hobotrashcan.com/2006/08/03/one-on-one-with-jonah-hill/ One on One with... Jonah Hill] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hobotrashcan.com/2006/08/03/one-on-one-with-jonah-hill/ |date=20201128051919 }}", ''Hobo Trashcan'', August 2006. Retrieved on June 29, 2007.</ref>。他的表演開始逐漸小發展，並使他更加堅信於電影裡演出這條路。希爾與著名演員[[達斯汀·霍夫曼|達斯汀·霍夫曼]]的孩子們成為朋友<ref name=":2" />，他們也引薦希爾給父親<ref name=":1" />。霍夫曼推薦下，要求他去參加電影《[[心靈偵探社|心靈偵探社]]》的演員徵選，而希爾最後也成功參與演出。

而後，希爾在[[賈德·阿帕托|賈德·阿帕托]]（Judd Apatow）執導長片《[[40處男|40處男]]》表現亮眼，而在導演的下部長片《[[好孕臨門|好孕臨門]]》得到主要配角的演出，以及在《[[命運好好玩|命運好好玩]]》飾演17歲的班傑明·紐曼，最後在艾帕托監製的《[[男孩我最壞|男孩我最壞]]》擔任主角。

[[File:Jonah_Hill_-_001.jpg|thumb]]]]

希爾曾參與《[[變形金剛：復仇之戰|變形金剛：復仇之戰]]》的演員徵選，作為一名[[西亞·李畢福|西亞·李畢福]]角色的夥伴<ref>{{cite news |author=Nicole Sperling |title=Jonah Hill no longer in talks for 'Transformers 2' |publisher=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2008-05-06 |url=http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2008/05/jonah-hill.html |accessdate=2008-05-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509022701/http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2008/05/jonah-hill.html |archivedate=2008-05-09 }}</ref>。下部電影演出賈德·艾帕托的第三部執導長片《[[命運好好笑|命運好好笑]]》，與[[亞當·山德勒|亞當·山德勒]]、[[艾瑞克·巴納|艾瑞克·巴納]]和[[塞斯·羅根|塞斯·羅根]]共同演出。同時身兼為2009年[[沙夏·拜倫·科恩|沙夏·拜倫·科恩]]偽紀錄片電影《[[G型教主|G型教主]]》的製片助理<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming | title = Trio joins Judd Apatow film | publisher = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2008-06-11 | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117987337.html?categoryid=13&cs=1 | accessdate = 2008-06-13 | archive-date = 2008-07-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080709034441/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117987337.html?categoryid=13&cs=1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2009年，希爾在[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]電台採訪時表示，儘管他的事業成功，他也不會感到倦怠。「我可以誠實地說，我不是在電影這塊領域上最有才華的人，但我或許是最明白它的。一天內總會有幾次簡直不敢相信現在我正在[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]宣傳我主演的電影，這出乎我本身預料之外。」<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.zmonline.com/WhosOn/MorningCrew/Highlights/Detail.aspx?id=15221#|title=Interview with ZM and Polly Gillespie|date=2010-06-14|accessdate=2010-06-15|publisher=[[ZM|ZM]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101201141938/http://zmonline.com/WhosOn/MorningCrew/Highlights/Detail.aspx?id=15221|archivedate=2010-12-01}}</ref>

=== 編劇 ===
希爾年輕時就想作一名[[編劇|編劇]]，夢想有天加入《[[辛普森家庭|辛普森家庭]]》、《[[週末夜現場|週末夜現場]]》和《賴瑞桑德斯秀》（The Larry Sanders Show）的編劇團隊<ref name="htc" />。一次機緣下，希爾藉由他的親密友人開始編寫劇本，首部作品《[[心靈偵探社|心靈偵探社]]》與[[傑森·薛茲曼|傑森·薛茲曼]]（Jason Schwartzman）共同演出<ref name="htc" />。
此外，他正在為[[索尼影業|索尼影業]]寫一部喜劇電影《''Pure Imagination''》，關於一名男子在經歷[[心理創傷|心理創傷]]後，發展出一個想像中的朋友。電影原預計於2008年著手進行，但至今為止仍在發展階段<ref>Carroll, Larry. "[http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/07/09/superbad-star-re-teams-with-apatow-for-imagination/ 'Superbad' Star Re-Teams With Apatow For 'Imagination'] {{Wayback|url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/07/09/superbad-star-re-teams-with-apatow-for-imagination/ |date=20150914115526 }}", ''[[MTV_News|MTV News]]'', 2007-07-09. Retrieved on July 11, 2007.</ref>。

